# VibeBoard CODEOWNERS
# ====================
# This file defines code ownership for automated review assignment.
# When a PR modifies files matching a pattern, the listed owners are
# automatically requested for review.
#
# Syntax: <pattern> <owner1> <owner2> ...
# Owners can be GitHub usernames (@user) or team names (@org/team)
#
# Last match wins - more specific patterns should come later.

